      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Swehtihts buhs tawas\nMeefas Anglis/ un tawas Sem-\nmes Anglis/ un tawu Lohpu An-\nglis/un tawu Wehrſchu Augums/\nun tawu fihtu Lohpu gannami\nPulki.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Swehtihts buhs taws Kur-\nwis/ un kas tew atleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Swehtihts buhſi tu ee-ee-\ndams/ un Swehtihts buhſi tu is-\needams.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS dohs wiſ-\nfus tawus Eenatneekus / kaſ\nprett tew zeltahs / ka tee tawá\nBreekscha tohp nokauti / pa wee-\nnu Zeltu tee prett tew isees/ un pa\nfepttieem Zelteem buhs teemi\nprecksch tewi behat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS pawehlehſ\ntam Swehtumain pahr tew / ka\ntas ar tew eſtohts tawás Klehtis/\nun eekſch wiſſa / pee ka tu tawu\nRohku issteepi / un Swehtihs tew\ntai Semmê / ko tas KUNGS\ntaws Deews tew dohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS tew eezels\nfew par SwehteemLaudim/ittin ka\nwiſſch tew Swehrejs irr/ ja tu ta\nKUNGA tawa Deewa Banſlus\nturreti/ un winna Zeltôs staigati.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad redsehs wiſſi Laudts\nwirs Semmes / ka tu pehz ta\nKUNGA Wahrdã noſaukts effi/\nun bihſees preeksch tew.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS tew fohti\nwairohs ar Labbumu/ pee tawas\nMeefas Angteem / un pee tawu\nLohpu Angteem / un pee tawas\nSemnes Angteem / wirs tahs\nSemmes/ ko tas KUNGS taws\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS atwehre-\nteiw fatwu labbu Mantu/ to Deb-\nbesfi/ ka tas tawai SemmetLee-\ntn dohd fawã Laikã / un fweht-\nwifſu tawu Rohkas Darbu/ un\ntew buhs daudſ Landim afsdoht/\nbet tu us Parradn ne atſxemfi-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS darrihe-\ntew par Galwn/un ne par Astu/\nun tu buhſi pa wiſſu ween / nn\nne pa appakſchu/ ja tu ta KUNG\nGA tawa Deewa Bausfleim\nklausifi / ko es tew ſchodeen pa-\nwehtu winnas turreht un darriht\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ne atkahyſi no wiſſeen\nteem Wahrdeem/ ko es juns ſcho-\ndeen pawehnu/ ne pa labbas ni\npa kreifas Rohkas/ zitteem Dee-\nweem pakkat dſihdainees wiſ-\nxuem kalpoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ja tu ta KUNGA\ntawa Deewa Balknet ne kla-\nfifi/ ka tu turri un darri wiſſu-\nwirra Bausſus/ un winna Lik-\nkumus / ko es tew ſchodeen pa-\nwehtu/ tad nahks wiſſas ſchib-\nNolahdefchanas pahr tew / un\ntew notiks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nolahdehts buhſi tu Bil-\nshta / un nolahdehts buhſi tu\nLaikã.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nolahdehts buhs taw-\nKurwis/ un kas tew atleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nolahdehts buhs tawas\nMeefas Anglis/ un tawas Sem-\nmes Anglis/ tawu Wehrſchu Au-\nguis/ un tawu fihtu Lohpu gan-\nnami Pulki.\n"
    }
  ],
